WEBVTT

00:11.895 --> 00:17.467
Wherever you go,
you will have fam’ly near.

00:17.467 --> 00:23.239
Because wherever you go,
Jehovah’s people are there.

00:23.239 --> 00:26.209
And you’ll feel love.

00:26.209 --> 00:32.215
You’ll feel love,
A brotherly love.

00:34.551 --> 00:39.222
So feel the love.

00:41.191 --> 00:52.202
Brothers and sisters all over the world
Unite with Jehovah and follow his Son

00:52.202 --> 00:57.140
To bring you love—
A nation of,

00:57.140 --> 01:07.450
Of brotherly love.
So feel the love.

01:15.658 --> 01:33.510
Our Father provides for us all—
No one left over.

01:33.510 --> 01:38.715
Deep in the jungle 
or on mountains high,

01:38.715 --> 01:44.354
In big, modern cities 
or on islands afar,

01:44.354 --> 01:52.762
You belong.
You belong to the people of God.

01:55.632 --> 01:59.636
So feel the love.

02:07.677 --> 02:25.094
Our Father provides for us all—
No, no one left over.

02:25.094 --> 02:36.472
But in the world, it can be cold—
A scary place, truth to be told.

02:36.472 --> 02:46.816
So how wonderful it is to know
The one true God and his people!

02:51.621 --> 02:56.626
Jesus, he taught 
his disciples to love.

02:56.626 --> 03:02.232
So millions of people, 
as a nation, they show

03:02.232 --> 03:10.006
Jehovah’s love— 
And you belong among all of them.

03:13.610 --> 03:17.313
So feel the love.

03:24.988 --> 03:43.099
So feel the love.
